Business Name: {{$json.name}}
Business Type: {{$json.type}}
Website: {{$json.website}}
Rating: {{$json.rating}}

If website or details are missing, intelligently infer from the business name and type.

Return ONLY valid JSON:
{
  "services": ["", ""],
  "summary": ""
}

Rules:
- services must list main offerings
- summary must be ONE natural sentence
- summary must be specific to the business
- DO NOT repeat the same phrasing
- DO NOT leave fields empty
- infer logically if data missing
- DO NOT include markdown
